Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:22.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沉睡的蓝色水之星 轻轻地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.46,0:00:31.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吻那点燃生命之火的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.23,0:00:36.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,称为时间的金色波纹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.31,0:00:44.87,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在宇宙之唇中诞生的叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.87,0:00:52.24,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埋在心中的温柔星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:56.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相唤起火焰……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.25,0:01:02.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同流离在波涛中的遇难船一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.43,0:01:07.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:16.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 现在有人正在寻找你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想与你相见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.23,0:22:48.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Oh 我禁不住相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.45,0:22:55.04,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}一定会和你再见面 从那天起就一直坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.04,0:23:00.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}一定能呼唤到你 如果你还有心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.42,0:23:10.80,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}无限的力量 将你唤醒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.80,0:23:16.43,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}啊 在你受到伤害前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.43,0:23:22.52,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}尽量 找寻 请
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.52,0:23:27.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}不要丢弃 正是因为在这痛苦的时期
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.40,0:23:31.01,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}总有一天会看见蔚蓝的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:38.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}一定的 直到和你一起看的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.58,0:01:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚伽玛秘密地在中立Side中继续进行补给
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.87,0:01:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪在这个卫星中遇到了罗莎米亚·巴达姆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这次相遇却让卡缪完全摸不到头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格利普斯始动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.99,0:02:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是人类为了在宇宙生活而建造的人工大地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙殖民卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.93,0:02:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的农业工厂各自控制太阳的日照
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.95,0:02:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,种植着一年中必需的各种农作物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.22,0:02:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.52,0:02:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得她有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.95,0:02:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不把哈罗还我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.71,0:02:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.41,0:02:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥你真坏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说好马上就回来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:02:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来介绍一下爱玛中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女孩究竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱玛小姐很温柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人…好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗莎米
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在害怕什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她去自省室休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等她冷静一点 我再问她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.71,0:03:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花 把她带到自省室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要听花的话哦 知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人会把哥哥抢走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.92,0:04:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.05,0:04:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.69,0:04:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格利普斯空域里大概有多少垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是施工时丢弃的金属和岩石之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们知道其数量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把格利普斯2号改造成激光发射器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那应该有相当多的岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格利普斯2号正从色当之门移动至攻击月球的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢弃的垃圾会自动分开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们真的把卫星改造成了光束炮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.22,0:04:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在需要我们去确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格利普斯1号和色当之门也需要查一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.11,0:04:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能过来 罗莎米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是自省室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不要责备花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.01,0:04:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的不对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有习惯这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:04:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 咱们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从第13号卫星上船的平民吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想请哈桑医生给她做一个仔细的检查
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗 卡缪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯瓦特罗大尉的意思是说 罗莎米是强化人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我没有那个意思 卡缪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.71,0:05:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗莎米 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的头…好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是哥哥的事还是你的事 都告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人好害怕 只是这样而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望得到灵魂上的安宁 所以才来这里的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂上的安宁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.97,0:06:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心灵明明伤痕累累
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但亚伽玛的男人们却完全没有察觉出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.46,0:06:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你不得不扮演一个坚强的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你筋疲力尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要一个治愈疲倦的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好像你亲眼所见一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的温暖 正是你所需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我说的都是假话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以拿刀刺向我的胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布提马斯·西洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候我不会反抗的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要驾驶帕拉斯·雅典娜回朱庇特利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅萨拉就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你随便用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格利普斯2号的空域 没有发现敌人确切的动静
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利克·迪亚斯 准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利克·迪亚斯 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达MKII 爱玛 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Z高达 卡缪 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有MS吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经叫巴扎姆队出击了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:07:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:08:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西洛克带来的女人在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是说蕾柯亚少尉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫那个女人也去侦察敌情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.39,0:08:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.57,0:08:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说叫她出击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 呼叫蕾柯亚少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那个女人的行动中或许可以知道西洛克的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚少尉归入哈米尔中尉指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪 你的速度太快了 显得不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的目的不是去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现MS的机影 要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关闭无线通信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Z
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚少尉 你发现什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连利克·迪亚斯也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚少尉 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在犹豫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经无法再回到奥古了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈米尔中尉 右下方发现MS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台机体是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是莎拉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪 任务优先 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪 前进
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈米尔中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.72,0:10:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你追上Z的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我 爱玛中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个声音…难道…怎么会呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.63,0:10:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把敌人的注意力吸引到这边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保证Z前往格利普斯的空域
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉你也去甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫增援的MS做好出击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:10:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二波 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射人员上来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要穿上标准服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身体不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗莎米
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗莎米 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.82,0:11:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.76,0:11:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁能给我一台MS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉 你什么时候才能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是Z
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.67,0:11:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:11:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等 坐在梅萨拉里的人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认错人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这种久违的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个机师是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:12:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚小姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你还活着啊 蕾柯亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪 很久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是任务吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜入提坦斯 刺探敌人的机密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心地真好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你错了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.76,0:13:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是自愿来到提坦斯的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我主动要做提坦斯的机师的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我经常听说 当间谍连自己人都得骗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.44,0:13:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪 我求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太任性了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你恨我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我刚才确实想用你来立功的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.96,0:13:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你明明活着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们却不得不以这种方式相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你成为敌人 这就意味我我们要互相残杀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要因为我而为难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:14:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我回到亚伽玛也是一无所有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不够资格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我至少能保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是既残忍又温柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 总有一天你会理解我变节的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不理解那种心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种近乎自杀的认真性格会永远纠缠住我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被认真的性格杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请打开舱门 蕾柯亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格利普斯2号的卫星光束炮已经完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去叫亚伽玛撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我求你了 请打开舱门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪开 卡缪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来吧 现在还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪 你见到蕾柯亚少尉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里都可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不仅不报告 还乱发什么脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对我这个孩子说些听不懂的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然会发脾气的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对哥哥做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是你这种人该来的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗莎米 你去和孩子们玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该杀死她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱玛中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是背叛了提坦斯的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的情况不能相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.25,0:16:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照自己的主义行动真的那么正确吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要自大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果凡事感情用事就能办到 那谁都会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是扇人耳光的人说出来的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.39,0:16:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.08,0:16:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有爱玛中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格利普斯2号的卫星光束炮已经完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个情报是可信的 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉 那种情报是不可靠的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我也相信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则 我们必死无疑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.45,0:16:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事是我们之间的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由你们知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是大人的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾啊 瞒着大家又有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.35,0:16:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:16:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照着大人的意思做就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会假装明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:16:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说我没有见到蕾柯亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说对我方不利的事情要忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是这么说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.85,0:17:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有花还像孩子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小看我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.21,0:17:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我是在夸你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈桑医生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪 你来跟她说 不用害怕 马上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我全身都很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是舰长的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.49,0:17:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫我检查这个女孩的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女孩可能是强化人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗莎米是强化人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不能肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是亚伽玛的船员很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样 做个仔细的检查 看她有没有病
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗莎米这个人 不是间谍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果在人际关系上造成互相猜忌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事关舰内的士气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.71,0:17:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉 我知道你背负着“前提坦斯成员”的重担
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.59,0:18:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于卡缪的事情 我正在反省
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.39,0:18:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你和亚伽玛的MS接触了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.21,0:18:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所属不明舰判断为亚伽玛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周边空域中没有其他舰影
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们打算突袭格利普斯2号吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.82,0:18:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星光束炮怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在准备部分试射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:18:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射角度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.96,0:19:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在瞄准Side 2的空域
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能瞄准亚伽玛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 卫星光束炮发射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要击中第13号卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能好好威胁一下奥古
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐 我告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 没有批准之前你要留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.25,0:19:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵官要适应提坦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离发射还有3分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格利普斯2号没有动静吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.44,0:19:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.90,0:19:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.09,0:19:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得太安静了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.56,0:19:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是不需要放出伪装的污染空域
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.60,0:19:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚的情报是真的 恐怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.31,0:19:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果卫星光束炮是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么它将瞄准Side 2或者月球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 第一级战斗配置
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格利普斯2号可能会使用卫星光束炮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.06,0:20:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我不要医生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 现在是第一级战斗配置
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.36,0:20:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须待在居住区里面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是医生很可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.38,0:20:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 我消失就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.88,0:20:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,40%临界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.53,0:20:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射前3
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.47,0:20:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋提坦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这束光是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲伤与痛苦交织在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Side 2的第18号卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.32,0:21:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有1枚镜片半毁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接击中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.63,0:21:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该有2个直径约200米的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.90,0:21:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星会解体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.55,0:21:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会解体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.59,0:21:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那帮家伙竟然做出了这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫MS队中止出击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.52,0:21:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰将全速离开这个空域
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝贺您 巴斯克大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.64,0:21:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果输出功率达到100%的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.17,0:21:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.15,0:21:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 无论是中立卫星还是月球上的那帮人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:21:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都会明白反抗我们提坦斯是毫无意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.52,0:22:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚伽玛撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.51,0:22:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我已经不能走回头路了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.57,0:22:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人的力量 是无法阻止那种事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.36,0:23:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在蕾柯亚指挥毒气攻击的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.46,0:23:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗莎米亚离开了亚伽玛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.08,0:23:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是罗莎米亚作为强化人而觉醒的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.18,0:24:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她察觉到卡缪驾驶的Z是自己的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.78,0:24:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士Zeta高达
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.99,0:24:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.60,0:24:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看见了时代之泪
